e The City Accountant and the General Services Officer (GSO) exert more efforts to reconcile their respective records of the PPE.
e The Inventory Committee conduct physical inventory of the PPE accounts in the General Fund (GF) and Special Education Fund (SEF) books with acquisition cost aggregating P27,808,320.50 to determine its actual existence and condition and prepare the corresponding RPCPPE;
 e The GSO provide detail of the property totaling P418,716,868.35 taken up in the RPCPPE in lump sum as beginning balances;
